England top Group One and will discover their opponents for next month’s qualifying play-offs when the draw is made next Friday.

Southgate, who has called up Middlesbrough’s Ben Gibson for the injured Spurs defender Eric Dier, will try to give most of his squad game time against Lithuania and Moldova.

